{"tid":1998672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情衝擊 德國失業人口單月暴增30萬","createTime":"2020-05-02T14:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T15:48:01.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a47507da8fd9b9268151e07ef051a9bf50b079","tid":1998672,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4531417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F4531417&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=f1126be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4531417</a><br />\n<br />\n德國官方今天公布的數據顯示，德國4月失業人口較3月暴增30萬，異乎尋常，凸顯2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫情對這個歐洲最大經濟體造成的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，根據德國聯邦勞工局（FederalLabour Agency）彙整的數據，德國4月失業人口飆升，從3月的230萬人暴增至260萬人。<br />\n<br />\n德國聯邦勞工局表示，本月經季節調整後的失業率，從前一個月的5.0%增至5.8%。<br />\n<br />\n德國聯邦勞工局局長謝勒（Detlef Scheele）發表聲明說：「冠狀病毒大流行，可能導致德國出現二次世界大戰後最嚴重衰退。&hellip;勞動力市場也會承壓。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，德國聯邦勞工局表示，約有75萬家企業申請讓總計1010萬名員工，納入政府資助的減少工時計畫。<br />\n<br />\n謝勒還說，德國聯邦勞工局登記的職缺數「徹底崩跌」，減少16萬9000個，降至62萬6000個職缺。<br />\n<br />\n德國聯邦衛生部轄下疾病控制機構「羅伯特‧科赫研究所」（Robert Koch Institute, RKI）今天公布的數據顯示，境內新增1478人確診武漢肺炎，累計確診來到15萬9119例。不治人數則增加173人，來到6288人。"},{"pid":"0a22aa1d8039e0423d75d8508f3710df57acc8be","tid":1998672,"uid":345524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"問中國索償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079b6b99186c0f4d30ea7deee54be3ebfea2e326","tid":1998672,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"all because of Wuhan and president xi<br />\nalles wegen Wuhan und Pr&auml;sident Schei&szlig;loch"},{"pid":"8a5c77002c17a425c31902fd9f6418fd2669d55a","tid":1998672,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:59:0